  m_Name: DialogNPCCavallier
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  Name: Toni
  Icon: {fileID: -2105629146, guid: d556a7f542c7d03429c5a535ce31a084, type: 3}
  HasInteraction: 0
  interactionType: 3
  Greeting: MARTO 11 LABS
  Day1Dialog:
  - 'I was up here when they came. The sea was already full of them. Galleys, as
    far as I could see.

    I thought the world was ending that morning.'
  Day2FirstTimeDialog:
  - "The drums of war\u2026 the war cries from their decks\u2026 the flags. I was
    scared. I still am.\nThey kept arriving \u2014 wave after wave. We stood here
    and watched them land at Marsaxlokk.\nNo one spoke. We all know the end is coming
    for us."
  Day2MetBeforeDialog:
  - "The drums of war\u2026 the war cries from their decks\u2026 the flags. I was
    scared. I still am.\nThey kept arriving \u2014 wave after wave. We stood here
    and watched them land at Marsaxlokk.\nNo one spoke. We all know the end is coming
    for us."
  Day3FirstTimeDialog:
  - "We started firing immediately on their ships. From that moment on, the cannons
    never stopped.\r\nBut they fired back. They set up their cannons on Mount opposite
    the fort. It looks down on us\u2014 that\u2019s why the cannonballs reach us.\r\nYou
    should speak to the Italian knight Paolo Avogadro. He knows the fort\u2026 and
    how both sides are fighting."
  Day3MetBeforeDialog:
  - "We started firing immediately on their ships. From that moment on, the cannons
    never stopped.\r\nBut they fired back. They set up their cannons on Mount opposite
    the fort. It looks down on us\u2014 that\u2019s why the cannonballs reach us.\r\nYou
    should speak to the Italian knight Paolo Avogadro. He knows the fort\u2026 and
    how both sides are fighting."
  Day4FirstTimeDialog:
  - "They killed my best friend! Shrapnel from one of the cannons - can't tell you
    if it was from ours or theirs.  There is chaos all around. He didn\u2019t make
    it. The infirmary never rests, but some wounds are too severe.\r\nSome are left
    to die.\r\nI still see him when I close my eyes. That\u2019s when I realised
    I was too young to be here\u2026 and too late to leave."
  Day4MetBeforeDialog:
  - "They killed my best friend! Shrapnel from one of the cannons - can't tell you
    if it was from ours or theirs.  There is chaos all around. He didn\u2019t make
    it. The infirmary never rests, but some wounds are too severe.\r\nSome are left
    to die.\r\nI still see him when I close my eyes. That\u2019s when I realised
    I was too young to be here\u2026 and too late to leave."
  Day5FirstTimeDialog:
  - "I don\u2019t think any of us were meant to survive this. \nI was here when it
    began. I\u2019ll be here when it ends.\nAt least I\u2019ll be remembered as a
    brave man."
  Day5MetBeforeDialog:
  - "I don\u2019t think any of us were meant to survive this. \nI was here when it
    began. I\u2019ll be here when it ends.\nAt least I\u2019ll be remembered as a
    brave man."
